27:39.000Z","msg":"笑死口就話唔撚驚 <br />\n點知原來二仔底 <br />\n一言一句都話比人知 自己淆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"佢個女係美國人,仲話住慣美國唔習慣香港生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/23637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F23637&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=105f58e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/23637</a><br />\n以前每逢學校假期，葉榮欣都會返港，在黨內做義工，大學畢業後更決定留港兩年，先幫母親打江山，<span class=\"red\">之後再返美國讀MBA</span>。她老實說：「<span class=\"red\">我覺得美國生活較適合我</span>，因為講英文，無人識我媽咪。留在香港是因為她，尖子人才好難留，我的作用會大過在美國。」<br />\n<br />\n代母出征<br />\n她今年七月正式受薪上班，每朝十時前返到公司，主力負責策劃和宣傳，收工後還要陪母親去宴會、飯局應酬。遇正母親有事未能出席，她更要代母出席，孤身上陣。問她是否習慣，她坦白說：「<span class=\"red\">永遠都不會慣，大家不同背景，其他人年紀大我好多，又要講好多中文。我十四歲去美國，英文好流利，好似母語，講中文就要諗吓。」</span>"},{"pid":"7849926c6441a2fcfbf195ef8a47bf480f37d19f","tid":2149293,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"c43b2f125a3235e78757cb87edf44fcae48ff5d2","tid":2149293,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e3587954eef29a071eee33550bd72ff00a93e91","tid":2149293,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb4ac9b3ff54d8d08605f8bef975ae43ee834c5","tid":2149293,"uid":282637,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"af774124db6610298b45a49f0c0625cadc8c4eb9","tid":2149293,"uid":34065,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"笑死口就話唔撚驚 <br />\n點知原來二仔底 <br />\n一言一句都話比人知 自己淆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />